title: Comparisons of Champs (As in pls give me champ names and types)
body:
Hello everyone,
Just wondering if you could be so kind as to give me some champs and their "types"
E.g Caitlyn is an Early Game Poke Champ, Vayne is a late game all in champ, leblanc is an early-mid burst champ etc.
Just wanted to compare how the types fared against each other is all.
Thank You!
